  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK528">
<l>potunōkkāṉ vēntaṉ varicaiyā nōkki </l>
<l>ṉatunōkki vāḻvār palar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Many relatives will live near a king, when they observe that he does not look on all alike, but that he looks on each man according to his merit.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
